<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC
  "-//Apache Software Foundation//DTD XDOC 1.0//EN"
  "http://maven.apache.org/dtd/xdoc_1_0.dtd">

<document>

  <properties>
    <title>Installation</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="How to install the taxonomy">
      <subsection name="Prerequisites">
        <p>
          These instruction assumes that you have an HST project based on the HST archetype, i.e.
          a Maven multi module project having modules cms, site and bootstrap.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Hippo Forge Maven 2 repository">
        <p>Add this repository to your root pom.xml (if not defined already):</p>
        <source><![CDATA[
<repository>
  <id>hippo-forge</id>
  <name>Hippo Forge maven 2 repository.</name>
  <url>http://maven.onehippo.com/maven2-forge/</url>
  <snapshots>
    <enabled>false</enabled>
  </snapshots>
  <releases>
    <updatePolicy>never</updatePolicy>
  </releases>
  <layout>default</layout>
</repository>]]></source>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="CMS Module">
        <p>Add the following dependencies to the pom of the project's CMS module.<br/>
          The versions are normally managed from the parent pom<code>org.onehippo.cms7:hippo-cms7-release</code> or the project's root pom.
        </p>
        <source><![CDATA[
<!-- Taxonomy -->
<dependency>
  <groupId>org.onehippo</groupId>
  <artifactId>taxonomy-api</artifactId>
</dependency>

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.onehippo</groupId>
  <artifactId>taxonomy-addon-frontend</artifactId>
</dependency>

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.onehippo</groupId>
  <artifactId>taxonomy-addon-repository</artifactId>
</dependency>]]></source>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Site Module">
        <p>Add the following dependencies to the pom of the project's site module.<br/>
          The versions are normally managed from the parent pom<code>org.onehippo.cms7:hippo-cms7-release</code> or the project's root pom.
        </p>
        <source><![CDATA[
  <dependency>
    <groupId>org.onehippo</groupId>
    <artifactId>taxonomy-api</artifactId>
  </dependency>

  <dependency>
    <groupId>org.onehippo</groupId>
    <artifactId>taxonomy-hst-api</artifactId>
  </dependency>

  <dependency>
    <groupId>org.onehippo</groupId>
    <artifactId>taxonomy-hstclient</artifactId>
  </dependency>]]></source>
      </subsection>
      <subsection>
        <p><span class="note">Note:</span> on <strong>Hippo 7.8</strong> and later, be sure to use startup option <code>-Drepo.bootstrap=true</code>
          for initializing the types, see
          <a href="http://www.onehippo.org/7_8/library/concepts/content-repository/content-bootstrap.html">Content Bootstrap</a></p>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>